setDetails.setDescription: HOBO with it's service hobotoken.com provides a burn mechanism to burn HoboNickels (HBN) UTXO coin. In return, users receive HoboNickels (HOBO) as ERC-20 tokens. The HOBO ERC-20 token will play a weighted role in future developments.
setDetails.managerDescription: HOBO is an ERC20 Token with 120M max supply. The contract has BURN ability to produce rarity.
